<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Purchase Confirmation</h1>

    <p>
      Dear <%= @order.billing_address.firstname.titleize %> <%= @order.billing_address.lastname.titleize %>,<br>
      Thank you for your purchase.
    </p>

    <p>
      Here we summarize the just made payment details:
    </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Amount paid:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@order.amount_to_pay) %><br>
    <strong>Payment channel:</strong>
    <% if @order.pay_type == "1"   %>
      PayPal
    <% elsif @order.pay_type == "2" %>
      Credit Card
    <% end %>
    <br>
    <strong>Transaction ID:</strong> <%= @order.transaction_id %>
  </p>

  <p>Print or archive this email as a receipt.</p>

  <p>If you want more information, you can call us on +39 0571 676176 or send an email to <a href="mailto:info@assaggiaolio.com">info@assaggiaolio.com</a></p>

  <p>
  This message was automatically generated, please do not respond.
  </p>

  <p>
    Best regards <br>
  Fara Vetrerie e Cristallerie Srl
  </p>
  <br>
  <p>
    <%= link_to "faravetrerie.it", "http://www.faravetrerie.it" %><br>
    <%= link_to "assaggiaolio.com", "http://www.assaggiaolio.com" %>
  </p>


  </body>
</html>
